        "Human": "menstrual cycle (human, elf). Phases: menstrual → follicular → ovulation → luteal (remainder).",
        "Feline": "induced ovulator (cat, rabbit). Phases: proestrus (menstrualDays) → estrus/waiting (ovulationDays) → interestrus (remainder). follicularDays = 0. Ovulation only fires on NotifyClimax.",
