        "fertilizationChance": "base per-egg probability of conception given normal sperm (3.0 units). Scaled by Fertilize(cum).",
        "phasedays_note": "menstrualDays + follicularDays + ovulationDays must be <= cycleThreshold. Remainder = final rest phase (luteal / diestrus+anestrus / interestrus)."
